column11: agriTech is a mobile application that helps farmers monitor their crops using AI image recognition. Farmers can take photos of their plants and get instant diagnosis of diseases and pest problems. The app provides treatment recommendations and connects farmers with agricultural experts. It also tracks weather conditions and suggests optimal planting and harvesting times based on local climate data.

column11: smartTransport is an IoT-based solution for optimizing public transportation routes in urban areas. The system uses real-time data from buses and passenger demand to suggest optimal routes and schedules. It includes a mobile app for passengers to track buses in real-time and plan their journeys more efficiently. The platform helps reduce waiting times and improves the overall public transport experience for commuters.
